
Title: Tomato Soup
Ingredients: Tomato (5 pieces), Onion (1 piece)
Instructions: Boil the tomatoes and onions, then blend them together.

Title: Chocolate Cake
Ingredients: Flour (2 cups), Cocoa powder (1 cup), Sugar (1.5 cups), Baking powder (1 tsp), Eggs (3 pieces), Milk (1 cup), Butter (0.5 cup), Vanilla extract (1 tsp)
Instructions: Preheat the oven to 350F (175C). Mix all the dry ingredients in one bowl. In another bowl, whisk the eggs, milk, melted butter, and vanilla extract. Combine both mixtures and pour the batter into a greased cake pan. Bake for 30-35 minutes or until a toothpick comes out clean.
